    name: "Biblical Hebrew: The Language Behind the Old Testament",
    summary:
      "The ancient Semitic language of the Hebrew Bible, with its root-based system, verbal aspect, and layers of meaning that no English translation can fully capture.",
    lensTags: ["academic", "protestant", "catholic", "jewish"],
