    name: "The Babylonian Exile: How Catastrophe Created Judaism",
    summary:
      "The destruction of Jerusalem in 586 BCE transformed a local temple cult into a portable, text-based religion that could survive anywhere.",
    lensTags: ["academic", "protestant"],
